You need to install several libraries before to compile the software.

---------------------------------------------------------------------
Please follow the instructions provided by the offical sites to 
install following library.

* CGAL

http://www.cgal.org/

* TCLAP

http://tclap.sourceforge.net/
---------------------------------------------------------------------

Modify *Makefile* in root directory, to make sure the configuration is 
correct. 

CC = gcc
CPP = g++ ##CPP compiler
CPPFLAGS = -Wall -I include 

LIBOPT = -lCGAL  -I/usr/local/include/tclap/ ##Library path


And type

make

to compile the whole software, this will generate a binary excutable 
one in the root directly:

MeshTK
